<br>
In a nutshell, I think folks need to treat their position on the list as their &quot;one shot&quot; at Ragefire, and should do whatever they possibly can, within reason, to be there when it's their turn.<br>
<br>
By mere virtue of this list existing, not to mention the overwhelming support the clerics have exhibited for each other, we have found that the cleric community consists of some pretty level-headed folks who have a great degree of compassion for their fellow man. That being said, I have no doubt that they will address any such situation, as it arises, in a fair manner.<br>
<br>
Let's keep the lines of communication open, try to stay in the chat channel when we're online, and keep each other abreast of our circumstances, while supporting one another in this camp, and I'm sure we'll be able to work out any problem together.<br>
<br>
